1
00:00:12,460 --> 00:00:15,160
[2012]

2
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:18,760
[8/17 Case]

3
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,280
Stop there! Freeze!

4
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:25,030
Stop there!

5
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:26,460
Stop there!

6
00:00:26,510 --> 00:00:26,920
Stop there!

7
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:27,640
Stop there!

8
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:30,320
Stop there!

9
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:32,920
No, no, no.

10
00:00:32,920 --> 00:00:33,200
Don't move!

11
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:33,600
Don't!

12
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:35,220
This is my first time here.
I don't know anything!

13
00:00:35,220 --> 00:00:36,350
Please spare me this time.

14
00:00:36,350 --> 00:00:37,070
Zhao Ning?

15
00:00:37,560 --> 00:00:38,520
Why are you here?

16
00:00:38,790 --> 00:00:39,430
Brother.

17
00:00:39,790 --> 00:00:40,920
Brother! Save me, please!

18
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:42,240
I'm scared. I don't know anything.

19
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:43,000
Silence!

20
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:44,060
Take them all away!

21
00:00:44,070 --> 00:00:44,530
Behave!

22
00:00:48,710 --> 00:00:50,430
Brother, save me. I'm scared.

23
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:52,110
Go!

24
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:58,560
Could you please help me plead

25
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,620
with Captain Zhou?

26
00:01:00,150 --> 00:01:02,200
He's just a kid who graduated
from college not long ago.

27
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:04,480
If he gets arrested,
his whole life will be ruined!

28
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:06,150
He's the only son in his family.

29
00:01:06,150 --> 00:01:07,790
They're all counting on him
to be successful.

30
00:01:07,790 --> 00:01:09,850
What will they do if he gets arrested?

31
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,760
L-Look, how about this?

32
00:01:12,950 --> 00:01:14,430
I... I'll release him secretly.

33
00:01:14,430 --> 00:01:15,680
Please pretend you see nothing.

34
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:16,920
I'm begging you.

35
00:02:35,530 --> 00:02:41,150
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

36
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:43,890
[Episode 20]

37
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,400
On the day

38
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,329
of the 8/17 Case,

39
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,170
I was there too.

40
00:02:52,940 --> 00:02:54,130
I feel so guilty.

41
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,770
Because of my selfishness,

42
00:02:57,630 --> 00:02:58,430
I've never had

43
00:02:58,430 --> 00:02:59,960
a day of peace ever since.

44
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,860
Your selfishness?

45
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,080
What is that?

46
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,030
Come here and explain it to me.

47
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:08,830
Don't come any closer, Zhou Jin!

48
00:03:09,250 --> 00:03:10,840
I beg you. Step back.

49
00:03:11,670 --> 00:03:12,730
Step back further!

50
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,560
Stop asking

51
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,960
and stop investigating, okay?

52
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:24,430
The dead can't come back to life.

53
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:27,890
Can you please just let go
of what happened to Chuan?

54
00:03:28,310 --> 00:03:30,710
Hengyun Logistics has been investigated.

55
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,280
The drug factory has been seized.

56
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,430
That's enough!

57
00:03:34,490 --> 00:03:36,960
Yao Weihai and Meng Junfeng
made a mistake.

58
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:38,800
They shouldn't have tried
to get to the bottom of it.

59
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:41,200
Why did they
have to mess with those people?

60
00:03:44,590 --> 00:03:46,240
I didn't do anything!

61
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:48,960
I just passed on some information to them.

62
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:50,800
I didn't go too far!

63
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:53,240
It has nothing to do with me!

64
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,870
Even without me,

65
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,870
they would find someone else!

66
00:03:56,870 --> 00:03:59,200
Yao Weihai and the others would still die!

67
00:03:59,370 --> 00:04:01,020
They would still die!

68
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:02,910
Zhao Ping.

69
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,880
I just have one question for you.

70
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,080
When those people

71
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:12,080
tortured and killed my brother,

72
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,160
were you there, too?

73
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:17,959
What did you see?

74
00:04:19,589 --> 00:04:20,300
How did

75
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,750
it happen?

76
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:25,520
That's a whole different thing.

77
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:26,980
Why on earth did my brother

78
00:04:29,610 --> 00:04:31,140
die such a miserable death?

79
00:04:33,980 --> 00:04:35,780
Zhou Jin, are you silly?

80
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,500
Do you seriously still believe

81
00:04:38,500 --> 00:04:40,900
Chuan's death resulted from the 8/17 Case?

82
00:04:41,190 --> 00:04:42,800
That's just the surface!

83
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,310
Who did it?

84
00:04:48,670 --> 00:04:49,520
Tell me.

85
00:04:51,420 --> 00:04:53,150
Who wanted to harm my brother?

86
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,120
Zhou Jin.

87
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:06,720
I will never let you know
in this lifetime.

88
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:09,640
Why?

89
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,180
Why would you say that?

90
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,600
Why do you know so much?

91
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:19,360
Were you also involved?

92
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:24,300
How could I possibly hurt Chuan?

93
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,040
In the whole SWAT team,

94
00:05:30,620 --> 00:05:32,620
Chuan was the one I admired the most.

95
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,310
He was a good person.

96
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:40,120
But what's the point
of being a good person?

97
00:05:41,940 --> 00:05:42,600
What a pity.

98
00:05:45,670 --> 00:05:46,520
What a pity.

99
00:05:48,190 --> 00:05:49,680
Don't come any closer!

100
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:50,950
Stay back!

101
00:05:50,970 --> 00:05:52,360
I'm begging you!

102
00:05:53,110 --> 00:05:54,110
Move back.

103
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,050
Back.

104
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,310
Zhou Jin.

105
00:06:05,430 --> 00:06:07,160
You are just like your brother.

106
00:06:08,430 --> 00:06:09,890
You're as gentle as he was.

107
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,280
Zhao Ping!

108
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:14,560
Don't act rashly.

109
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,400
Calm down!

110
00:06:15,430 --> 00:06:16,740
Don't do anything stupid!

111
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:17,500
Calm down.

112
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:18,440
Just calm down.

113
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:20,880
Come back, okay?

114
00:06:21,310 --> 00:06:22,170
Come back here.

115
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:23,920
Senior.

116
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,520
I wanted to attend your wedding.

117
00:06:37,630 --> 00:06:38,600
Zhao Ping!

118
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,110
Zhao Ping.

119
00:06:50,620 --> 00:06:51,250
Zhao Ping.

120
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,270
Chief Tan,

121
00:07:07,890 --> 00:07:09,690
I've gotten out of Guangqi Bank.

122
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,160
I've sent the backup to the team.

123
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,760
I have the USB drives with me.

124
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:14,960
Is there any footage of the deals in it?

125
00:07:14,980 --> 00:07:15,450
Yes,

126
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:16,190
plenty.

127
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:17,720
I think we can apply for an arrest warrant

128
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,120
and catch them directly.

129
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,240
Um, Chief Tan.

130
00:07:20,890 --> 00:07:22,550
How is everything on your end?

131
00:07:22,740 --> 00:07:24,000
Is it really Zhao Ping?

132
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:31,560
Yes.

133
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:50,070
Let's go back.

134
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:58,310
Bai Yang and the others have already found

135
00:07:58,310 --> 00:07:59,310
those USB drives.

136
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:03,900
It proves the high value
of Jiang Cheng's evidence.

137
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:06,240
I will talk to the leaders again

138
00:08:06,530 --> 00:08:07,930
and make an application,

139
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:11,220
trying to restore his identity
as soon as possible.

140
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:13,490
Actually, the fingerprint on the gun

141
00:08:13,870 --> 00:08:15,000
can't convict him.

142
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:17,480
Since we can't convict him,

143
00:08:17,890 --> 00:08:19,220
he can only be protected

144
00:08:19,390 --> 00:08:21,040
as an important witness

145
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:24,130
instead of being identified as a suspect.

146
00:08:26,310 --> 00:08:27,270
Thank you, Sir.

147
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:30,900
How about this?

148
00:08:31,830 --> 00:08:32,750
Later, I'll find someone

149
00:08:32,750 --> 00:08:34,750
to give you psychological counseling.

150
00:08:34,750 --> 00:08:35,880
Until we can confirm

151
00:08:36,590 --> 00:08:38,520
that you are in a good mental state,

152
00:08:39,409 --> 00:08:40,940
don't do fieldwork for now.

153
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,030
I'm fine, Sir.

154
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,370
Just do as I said.

155
00:09:17,910 --> 00:09:18,640
You're back.

156
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,540
What are you doing?

157
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:30,890
I'm exhausted.

158
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:35,240
I need to recharge.

159
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:40,130
Are you hungry?

160
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:42,510
Yes.

161
00:09:43,870 --> 00:09:45,470
I'm craving instant noodles

162
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,260
with a slice of cheese,

163
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:49,960
luncheon meat,

164
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:51,840
and an egg.

165
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:55,040
And I want one more cold beer.

166
00:09:57,630 --> 00:09:58,030
Okay.

167
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,580
I'll go make it.

168
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:09,390
Today...

169
00:10:12,870 --> 00:10:14,330
we went to catch Zhao Ping.

170
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,440
You knew it.

171
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,320
Professor Jiang,

172
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,400
I think it's time

173
00:10:29,750 --> 00:10:31,150
to root this person out.

174
00:10:31,780 --> 00:10:33,380
What do you think, Chief Tan?

175
00:10:33,410 --> 00:10:35,410
To catch a thief, you need evidence.

176
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,790
Spread the news about the USB drives

177
00:10:37,790 --> 00:10:39,080
to the team.

178
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:40,840
Say that the whole list

179
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,370
of visitors is stored in it.

180
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:43,930
Once knowing it,

181
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,850
the mole will try to destroy

182
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:48,150
the evidence before us by all means.

183
00:10:48,910 --> 00:10:49,970
I will send someone

184
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,080
to monitor him the whole time.

185
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,210
Once he makes a move,

186
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:55,840
we'll make an arrest immediately.

187
00:10:57,150 --> 00:10:58,750
Chief Tan, you're calling me

188
00:10:59,150 --> 00:11:00,750
not because you don't have a plan,

189
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:01,440
but because you are

190
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:04,100
considering who should
carry out this mission.

191
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,390
I find that I can't

192
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:08,130
hide anything from you.

193
00:11:08,680 --> 00:11:10,210
Zhou Jin will do a great job.

194
00:11:12,270 --> 00:11:12,790
Okay.

195
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:14,960
Hearing you say that,

196
00:11:15,510 --> 00:11:16,360
I'm relieved.

197
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:18,200
Also,

198
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,480
keep an eye on Jiang Cheng's safety

199
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,910
in case someone tries to silence him.

200
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:23,550
I got it.

201
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:24,800
Rest assured.

202
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:26,630
Professor Jiang,

203
00:11:27,550 --> 00:11:28,390
I think

204
00:11:29,910 --> 00:11:31,640
you are a very generous person.

205
00:11:32,550 --> 00:11:33,210
Good night.

206
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,120
Zhao Ping.

207
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:44,480
He died.

208
00:11:46,530 --> 00:11:47,290
He died?

209
00:11:52,450 --> 00:11:53,980
He didn't want to go to jail,

210
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:57,780
so he jumped off the building.

211
00:12:00,670 --> 00:12:02,750
I wanted to catch him.

212
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:06,200
But I didn't get the chance.

213
00:12:08,790 --> 00:12:09,920
It's not your fault.

214
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,390
I should have

215
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,910
gotten to know him better.

216
00:12:19,190 --> 00:12:20,950
I found out too late.

217
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,500
But over the past year,

218
00:12:26,510 --> 00:12:28,630
I met him almost every day.

219
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,480
Someone who wants to hide

220
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,430
can hide very well.

221
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,840
Was I so focused

222
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,080
on my brother's case

223
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:47,600
that I ignored the people
and things around me?

224
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:49,750
Be it friends

225
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,320
or family,

226
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:56,160
I cared too little about them.

227
00:12:57,760 --> 00:13:00,140
How long has it been
since you called home last time?

228
00:13:00,140 --> 00:13:01,060
I forgot.

229
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,910
But it was because I was afraid

230
00:13:04,510 --> 00:13:06,510
that they would ask what I was doing.

231
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:07,920
I didn't want to lie.

232
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:13,680
Let's go back and visit them in a while.

233
00:13:14,150 --> 00:13:15,150
I've been craving

234
00:13:15,570 --> 00:13:17,570
the waxberry wine your parents made

235
00:13:17,750 --> 00:13:19,210
the last time we went home.

236
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:27,550
As soon as I got

237
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:29,060
these USB drives from Guangqi Bank,

238
00:13:29,060 --> 00:13:30,720
I confirmed the contents

239
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,150
with Jiang Cheng right away

240
00:13:32,150 --> 00:13:33,670
and did a technical appraisal.

241
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:36,200
The contents inside
haven't been post-edited

242
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,930
and are completely authentic.

243
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:39,440
There are multiple videos
on the USB drives,

244
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:41,320
involving several famous cases

245
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:42,240
in Jingzhou,

246
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:43,790
including human trafficking,

247
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:45,960
smuggling, and drug trafficking.

248
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:47,970
The solving of these cases

249
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:50,550
more or less involved Comrade Yao Weihai.

250
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:51,870
I believe

251
00:13:52,270 --> 00:13:53,480
that in this case,

252
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:54,580
Cangfeng

253
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,840
must have played a very crucial role

254
00:13:56,930 --> 00:13:59,530
in the process
of investigating the evidence.

255
00:13:59,750 --> 00:14:01,110
The whereabouts of Qi Yan and the others

256
00:14:01,110 --> 00:14:02,180
still remain unclear

257
00:14:02,180 --> 00:14:03,550
and under investigation.

258
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:06,390
But according to the information
provided by Jiang Cheng,

259
00:14:06,390 --> 00:14:08,360
the Municipal Criminal Investigation Unit
and Nancheng Branch

260
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:10,510
have both sent plenty of officers
to thoroughly investigate

261
00:14:10,510 --> 00:14:11,440
the persons

262
00:14:11,470 --> 00:14:13,640
and institutions
connected to Hengyun Logistics.

263
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:15,900
I believe the results will come out soon.

264
00:14:16,070 --> 00:14:18,870
Comrade Yao Weihai realized
that his life might be

265
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:21,380
in danger during the Jingang Operation,

266
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,670
so he finally sent me

267
00:14:23,790 --> 00:14:25,150
a short message,

268
00:14:25,550 --> 00:14:28,790
handing over the phone numbers and a set

269
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:30,540
of communication methods

270
00:14:30,910 --> 00:14:32,370
between him and Cangfeng.

271
00:14:32,390 --> 00:14:34,150
At first, it was Comrade Jiang Cheng

272
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:35,960
who took the initiative to contact us.

273
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,440
I couldn't confirm his identity

274
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,840
as Cangfeng at that time.

275
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,660
After consulting Director Lu

276
00:14:40,690 --> 00:14:42,330
and Professor Jiang,

277
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:44,490
we conducted 2 tentative inspections

278
00:14:44,670 --> 00:14:45,840
on him.

279
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:48,240
The tip-off was accurate

280
00:14:48,510 --> 00:14:49,440
and safe.

281
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:51,150
That's why we carried out

282
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:53,280
the Kuangshan operation later.

283
00:14:53,680 --> 00:14:56,200
In addition, before the Jingang operation,

284
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:57,540
Comrade Yao Weihai

285
00:14:57,710 --> 00:15:00,160
gave me a small note,

286
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,190
saying,

287
00:15:01,270 --> 00:15:04,360
"On October 3rd, at Jingang Wharf,

288
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:05,410
make an arrest."

289
00:15:05,790 --> 00:15:07,190
And he told me personally

290
00:15:07,630 --> 00:15:09,870
that this intelligence came

291
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:13,000
from the undercover agent Cangfeng.

292
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:15,000
Later, we did a handwriting analysis,

293
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:17,130
and it was Jiang Cheng's handwriting.

294
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:19,030
Everyone, please look. This is

295
00:15:19,430 --> 00:15:21,690
the forensic report on the handwriting.

296
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:32,750
In November 2012,

297
00:15:32,750 --> 00:15:35,080
I joined the Cangfeng Special Operation.

298
00:15:35,630 --> 00:15:37,960
At that time, Leader Yao found

299
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:40,240
an illegal trading chain from the clue

300
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:42,270
about the suspects of the 8/17 Case.

301
00:15:42,630 --> 00:15:44,480
To catch all the people
involved in this trading chain

302
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:45,550
in one fell swoop,

303
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:48,440
Leader Yao arranged for me
to start with He Wen,

304
00:15:49,150 --> 00:15:50,440
make contact with He Wu,

305
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:52,240
and infiltrate the crime group.

306
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:53,510
As I said before,

307
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:55,300
it took us the whole 5 years

308
00:15:55,440 --> 00:15:58,100
to figure out
their organizational structure.

309
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,260
This trading chain

310
00:15:59,550 --> 00:16:01,010
exists not only in Haizhou

311
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,560
but also in Jingzhou.

312
00:16:03,180 --> 00:16:05,660
He Wu's in charge of the Haizhou area.

313
00:16:06,330 --> 00:16:08,400
And the criminal mastermind,
Old Scorpion, is the one

314
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:11,400
actually holding sway
over the entire trading chain.

315
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:13,240
The fingerprint on the murder weapon used

316
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:15,800
to shoot Yao Weihai
and Meng Junfeng has been identified

317
00:16:15,800 --> 00:16:16,680
as yours.

318
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:18,090
Jiang Cheng,

319
00:16:18,910 --> 00:16:20,120
we now require you

320
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:22,120
to honestly state what happened

321
00:16:23,030 --> 00:16:24,690
after the Jingang Operation.

322
00:16:33,690 --> 00:16:35,890
I didn't go to Jingang Wharf that day.

323
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:38,080
He Wu arranged for me to go

324
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,880
to a warehouse on Jiangbei Road.

325
00:16:41,210 --> 00:16:42,410
How many people went?

326
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:43,630
Two.

327
00:16:43,990 --> 00:16:45,630
Me and a young friend of mine.

328
00:16:46,720 --> 00:16:47,920
His name is Lei Dahua.

329
00:16:48,790 --> 00:16:50,150
Sirs, at this point,

330
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:52,610
I'd like to add something
before I continue.

331
00:16:52,790 --> 00:16:54,870
This young friend of mine, Lei Dahua,

332
00:16:54,890 --> 00:16:56,910
has never directly participated

333
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:58,140
in any criminal operations

334
00:16:58,140 --> 00:16:59,540
of Old Scorpion's group.

335
00:16:59,540 --> 00:17:01,810
And he covered for me to keep me safe

336
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:04,000
in dangerous situations many times.

337
00:17:04,359 --> 00:17:06,359
So I hope you can be lenient

338
00:17:06,660 --> 00:17:07,500
with him.

339
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:11,400
We'll discuss the situation

340
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:13,470
you mentioned after the meeting.

341
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:15,880
You may continue.

342
00:17:16,930 --> 00:17:19,260
After I arrived at the warehouse that day,

343
00:17:19,530 --> 00:17:22,460
there was an old guy named Qi
overseeing everything.

344
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:23,880
At first, I thought

345
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:25,160
he was Old Scorpion.

346
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:28,000
At that time,
he was playing chess with Meng Junfeng.

347
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,180
At the end of the game,

348
00:17:29,180 --> 00:17:30,970
he took out Yao's photo.

349
00:17:31,510 --> 00:17:33,040
Not until then did I realize

350
00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:34,780
that it was a trap.

351
00:17:35,270 --> 00:17:37,470
There was no so-called drug deal at all.

352
00:17:38,310 --> 00:17:39,270
They suspected there was

353
00:17:39,270 --> 00:17:40,930
an undercover cop among them.

354
00:17:41,270 --> 00:17:42,750
So they leaked this fake news

355
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:45,200
to the newcomers who just joined them.

356
00:17:45,750 --> 00:17:47,210
These newcomers included

357
00:17:47,590 --> 00:17:48,740
Meng Junfeng and me.

358
00:17:53,410 --> 00:17:54,200
I quit.

359
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,060
Are you scared?

360
00:17:56,630 --> 00:17:58,490
You even dare to catch the police.

361
00:17:59,350 --> 00:18:00,680
I've made it very clear.

362
00:18:01,570 --> 00:18:03,030
I'm here to make a fortune.

363
00:18:03,220 --> 00:18:05,080
I don't want to cause any trouble.

364
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:09,870
Trouble?

365
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:14,750
Do you know the 8.17 Case?

366
00:18:16,510 --> 00:18:17,720
Have you heard of it?

367
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:21,270
I led the team to do it.

368
00:18:23,110 --> 00:18:25,710
But there's a detail
you certainly don't know.

369
00:18:27,030 --> 00:18:28,070
Yao Weihai

370
00:18:29,830 --> 00:18:32,160
killed someone he shouldn't have killed.

371
00:18:41,040 --> 00:18:41,810
Today,

372
00:18:42,870 --> 00:18:44,550
you can survive

373
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:48,640
only if you kill him.

374
00:18:51,470 --> 00:18:53,600
It happened so suddenly

375
00:18:53,960 --> 00:18:55,920
that I really had no time and no way

376
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:57,720
to inform Leader Yao of all this,

377
00:18:57,810 --> 00:19:00,210
and couldn't cancel the operation in time.

378
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:03,620
You all know

379
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,090
what happened next.

380
00:19:05,840 --> 00:19:07,250
They kept Yao Weihai under control.

381
00:19:07,250 --> 00:19:08,980
The police also found us there.

382
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:11,360
They didn't care
about their underlings at all,

383
00:19:11,360 --> 00:19:14,160
pushing out some cannon fodder
to block the police

384
00:19:14,250 --> 00:19:16,850
and letting the major figures
evacuate first.

385
00:19:18,320 --> 00:19:20,320
Why did you act alone later?

386
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:25,260
Because the police moved all of a sudden

387
00:19:25,260 --> 00:19:26,720
and caught them off guard.

388
00:19:27,040 --> 00:19:28,000
When pulling out,

389
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,640
they didn't see their sniper,

390
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:31,440
so they arranged for me to go to his aid.

391
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:32,590
I only knew later

392
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:33,830
that the sniper was

393
00:19:33,830 --> 00:19:35,440
their real boss.

394
00:19:36,270 --> 00:19:37,160
He is Qi Yan,

395
00:19:37,560 --> 00:19:39,190
the one we call Old Scorpion.

396
00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:41,520
What was the scene like

397
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,600
when you first met Qi Yan?

398
00:19:45,090 --> 00:19:47,290
It was Zhou Jin from the Nancheng Branch

399
00:19:47,370 --> 00:19:48,000
who blocked him

400
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,550
in an abandoned factory.

401
00:19:50,090 --> 00:19:51,860
Zhou Jin used to be my fiancée.

402
00:19:52,350 --> 00:19:53,720
Because of the special situation
at that time,

403
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:55,640
I didn't tell her my identity.

404
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:57,750
However,

405
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,350
they caught Yao Weihai.

406
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:00,680
I was afraid that my identity

407
00:20:00,680 --> 00:20:01,940
might also be exposed,

408
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:03,930
so I had a few extra words with her.

409
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,110
I thought,

410
00:20:05,870 --> 00:20:06,780
in case I died,

411
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:09,440
she might understand what I was saying.

412
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:10,500
Zhou Jin has already reported

413
00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:12,020
what you said to her.

414
00:20:12,510 --> 00:20:15,240
Please continue
with what happened afterwards.

415
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,040
Cheng,

416
00:20:27,270 --> 00:20:28,000
are you okay?

417
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:40,640
Did you clean up the tail?

418
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,420
Isn't it enough that we saved you?

419
00:20:42,420 --> 00:20:43,480
Just cut the crap.

420
00:20:46,550 --> 00:20:47,810
Where is Old Scorpion?

421
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:51,790
No rush.

422
00:20:52,660 --> 00:20:53,590
You will see him.

423
00:20:55,590 --> 00:20:56,160
How is it?

424
00:20:56,190 --> 00:20:57,050
Is the game fun?

425
00:20:58,920 --> 00:20:59,780
Pretty boring.

426
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:01,750
Why not focus on making money

427
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:04,150
instead of insisting on risking our lives?

428
00:21:08,790 --> 00:21:09,640
Jiang Cheng.

429
00:21:10,590 --> 00:21:12,190
You live too pragmatically.

430
00:21:13,560 --> 00:21:14,670
Sometimes,

431
00:21:15,310 --> 00:21:16,710
spiritual satisfaction

432
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:19,440
matters more than material wealth.

433
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:24,080
So your spiritual satisfaction is
killing police officers?

434
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:26,670
What? Can't it be?

435
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:28,240
I just enjoy it.

436
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:29,920
Psychopath.

437
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,190
Cheng!

438
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:35,850
Mind your language.

439
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:37,810
I can blow your mouth off, you know?

440
00:21:54,960 --> 00:21:56,760
You remind me of a friend of mine.

441
00:21:57,750 --> 00:21:59,280
A very interesting friend.

442
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:01,410
He once called me that, too.

443
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:04,310
"Psychopath."

444
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:08,920
Do you know what happened
to him in the end?

445
00:22:10,040 --> 00:22:11,500
Did he also save your life?

446
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,800
Jiang Cheng, you are quite cute.

447
00:22:22,920 --> 00:22:24,720
Thank you for saving me just now,

448
00:22:25,110 --> 00:22:25,840
Jiang Cheng.

449
00:22:27,360 --> 00:22:28,040
Xing,

450
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:29,650
forgive him.

451
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:30,930
Jiang Cheng is new here

452
00:22:30,930 --> 00:22:32,460
and not quite used to it yet.

453
00:22:32,600 --> 00:22:33,600
Psychopath.

454
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:39,350
Let's go.

455
00:22:39,840 --> 00:22:41,430
The game has just begun.

456
00:22:52,720 --> 00:22:53,350
Enough!

457
00:22:54,690 --> 00:22:56,020
Don't beat him to death.

458
00:23:12,750 --> 00:23:13,410
Leader Yao,

459
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:16,120
hope you've been doing well.

460
00:23:19,590 --> 00:23:20,750
Qi Yan.

461
00:23:21,460 --> 00:23:22,830
It really is you.

462
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:25,300
What did Jiang Hansheng tell you?

463
00:23:26,110 --> 00:23:27,070
Qi Yan is dead.

464
00:23:27,960 --> 00:23:29,130
I am not Qi Yan.

465
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:33,200
I am here to avenge him.

466
00:23:33,910 --> 00:23:34,550
Come on.

467
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:37,240
Let's have a talk.

468
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,110
Back then,

469
00:23:39,350 --> 00:23:42,350
someone shot Qi Yan to death.

470
00:23:42,550 --> 00:23:43,370
Was it you

471
00:23:44,550 --> 00:23:45,830
or Jiang Hansheng?

472
00:23:48,960 --> 00:23:49,820
How about this?

473
00:23:50,810 --> 00:23:52,540
As long as you say it wasn't you,

474
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:54,680
I will let you go.

475
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,270
How's it?

476
00:24:00,030 --> 00:24:01,260
I fired the shot.

477
00:24:01,600 --> 00:24:02,320
No, no.

478
00:24:02,850 --> 00:24:03,350
Leader Yao,

479
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:05,110
maybe you don't get me.

480
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:08,400
I mean, as long as you say it wasn't you,

481
00:24:09,070 --> 00:24:10,830
and you had nothing to do with it,

482
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:12,160
I'll let you go.

483
00:24:13,530 --> 00:24:14,480
It was me.

484
00:24:17,100 --> 00:24:19,560
Leader Yao, it wasn't you
who fired the shot,

485
00:24:19,620 --> 00:24:21,580
right? This is the truth.

486
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:24,090
Jiang Hansheng did it,

487
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:25,590
right?

488
00:24:26,110 --> 00:24:27,970
You only need to tell the truth.

489
00:24:28,740 --> 00:24:29,870
Come on, Leader Yao.

490
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:30,950
Please!

491
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:43,380
So boring.

492
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:49,140
Since you don't want to make it out alive,

493
00:24:49,380 --> 00:24:50,770
play a game with me.

494
00:24:51,680 --> 00:24:52,400
Leader Yao,

495
00:24:53,350 --> 00:24:55,280
you've been tracking us for years,

496
00:24:55,750 --> 00:24:57,680
sending spies one after another.

497
00:24:58,310 --> 00:24:59,070
They came

498
00:24:59,960 --> 00:25:01,020
and died one by one.

499
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:07,320
Don't you feel heartbroken?

500
00:25:08,070 --> 00:25:09,430
Of course, I understand.

501
00:25:09,430 --> 00:25:10,880
You are a cop.

502
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:13,030
This is your duty.

503
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:15,800
Then I hope you can understand

504
00:25:17,310 --> 00:25:18,710
that catching this spy is

505
00:25:19,630 --> 00:25:21,260
my duty.

506
00:25:22,550 --> 00:25:23,750
Now tell me.

507
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:26,130
Who exactly is

508
00:25:27,230 --> 00:25:28,520
the spy you sent?

509
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,130
You?

510
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:35,960
Boss, Boss, it's not me.

511
00:25:36,500 --> 00:25:37,130
It's not me.

512
00:25:37,130 --> 00:25:37,850
You?

513
00:25:37,880 --> 00:25:38,360
Boss.

514
00:25:38,380 --> 00:25:40,180
Boss, please don't joke around.

515
00:25:41,350 --> 00:25:42,720
Boss, it's really not me.

516
00:25:42,720 --> 00:25:44,000
I really know nothing!

517
00:25:47,750 --> 00:25:48,400
You?

518
00:25:51,030 --> 00:25:52,160
Or...

519
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:55,590
you?

520
00:25:58,750 --> 00:25:59,830
Before the deal,

521
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:01,990
only these 5 guys knew about it.

522
00:26:02,720 --> 00:26:03,440
Leader Yao,

523
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,680
point out the spy,

524
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:09,160
and I'll make it quick for you, I promise.

525
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:09,890
How about it?

526
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:11,350
Leader Yao.

527
00:26:14,200 --> 00:26:15,800
It's fine if you don't say it.

528
00:26:16,590 --> 00:26:17,680
Killing 1 is the same

529
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:18,910
as killing 5.

530
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,880
I don't care.

531
00:26:21,470 --> 00:26:22,640
Say it!

532
00:26:22,720 --> 00:26:24,440
Say it! Say it now!

533
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:26,440
You old thing,
are you going to get us killed?

534
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:27,790
Hurry up and say it!

535
00:26:27,830 --> 00:26:29,270
Tell him!

536
00:26:29,270 --> 00:26:30,310
Enough!

537
00:26:30,330 --> 00:26:31,400
Stop yelling!

538
00:26:36,830 --> 00:26:38,490
Don't you two want to explain?

539
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,980
Godfather, what on earth is going on?

540
00:26:45,490 --> 00:26:46,670
Jiang Cheng.

541
00:26:49,280 --> 00:26:51,740
Would you believe me
if I said I'm not the spy?

542
00:26:54,960 --> 00:26:57,760
Boss He, are you just going to watch
and do nothing?

543
00:27:05,090 --> 00:27:06,690
You're really a psychopath.

544
00:27:07,070 --> 00:27:08,870
If you want to kill me, just do it.

545
00:27:11,680 --> 00:27:12,310
All right,

546
00:27:12,530 --> 00:27:13,570
as you wish.

547
00:27:14,800 --> 00:27:15,600
Kill them all.

548
00:27:16,830 --> 00:27:17,540
Boss!

549
00:27:24,730 --> 00:27:26,340
Leader Yao, don't blame me.

550
00:27:26,370 --> 00:27:27,390
I don't want to die.

551
00:27:27,390 --> 00:27:28,450
I don't want to die.

552
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:29,110
Xing,

553
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:30,600
please don't shoot.

554
00:27:31,430 --> 00:27:33,690
Godfather! Godfather, I'm begging you.

555
00:27:33,730 --> 00:27:35,300
Please give me one last chance.

556
00:27:35,300 --> 00:27:36,160
I promise I'll serve you devotedly.

557
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:37,130
I really misjudged you.

558
00:27:37,130 --> 00:27:38,690
Stand up!

559
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:40,240
You are a cop!

560
00:27:40,580 --> 00:27:41,490
Cangfeng!

561
00:27:41,730 --> 00:27:43,050
Hold on to your faith!

562
00:27:43,270 --> 00:27:44,160
Don't be scared of them!

563
00:27:44,160 --> 00:27:45,720
Stop talking! Shut up!

564
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:47,230
Godfather,

565
00:27:47,590 --> 00:27:48,930
please give me one last chance.

566
00:27:48,930 --> 00:27:50,350
I'm begging you, Godfather.

567
00:27:50,350 --> 00:27:51,590
I swear I'll serve you wholeheartedly.

568
00:27:51,590 --> 00:27:52,830
I don't want to die.

569
00:27:54,330 --> 00:27:54,990
Godfather,

570
00:27:55,500 --> 00:27:57,650
I beg you. Please give me one last chance.

571
00:27:57,650 --> 00:27:58,890
How come it's you?

572
00:27:59,570 --> 00:28:00,350
Sorry.

573
00:28:04,590 --> 00:28:06,630
I could tell from Yao's look

574
00:28:07,510 --> 00:28:10,110
that Meng Junfeng
exposed himself on purpose.

575
00:28:10,110 --> 00:28:12,090
He either knew about my existence

576
00:28:12,110 --> 00:28:13,910
or figured out

577
00:28:14,500 --> 00:28:16,020
I was also a spy sent by Yao.

578
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:19,880
No wonder you kept making mistakes

579
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:22,270
and giving me bad luck
for the past year and a half.

580
00:28:22,270 --> 00:28:23,960
So you are the mole.

581
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:28,160
At that critical time,

582
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:30,550
he was the one who stepped up

583
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:32,430
and saved me.

584
00:28:40,350 --> 00:28:41,440
Sirs,

585
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:43,460
I have finished my report.

586
00:28:43,590 --> 00:28:44,790
I didn't kill anyone.

587
00:28:46,350 --> 00:28:48,550
It was Old Scorpion who got them killed.

588
00:28:49,280 --> 00:28:50,720
The reason I'm alive is

589
00:28:51,550 --> 00:28:53,680
that Meng Junfeng took the fall for me.

590
00:28:54,750 --> 00:28:55,510
Jiang Cheng,

591
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:58,530
what about the fingerprint on the gun?

592
00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:00,830
They gave me the gun

593
00:29:00,830 --> 00:29:02,870
and asked me to dispose of the bodies.

594
00:29:02,870 --> 00:29:05,270
The fingerprint was left on it
at that time.

595
00:29:05,750 --> 00:29:07,950
I could have wiped the fingerprint off.

596
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:09,200
But I thought,

597
00:29:10,050 --> 00:29:12,310
since I had lost contact with the police,

598
00:29:12,900 --> 00:29:14,620
if the police could focus

599
00:29:14,650 --> 00:29:17,580
their attention on me again
due to this fingerprint,

600
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:19,080
it might be a good thing.

601
00:29:21,160 --> 00:29:21,590
Okay,

602
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,460
we have no more questions.

603
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:26,120
After verification,

604
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,110
the situation

605
00:29:27,110 --> 00:29:29,830
of Cangfeng operation
having double-line Investigators was

606
00:29:29,830 --> 00:29:32,190
filed as a confidential record

607
00:29:32,210 --> 00:29:34,720
in the Provincial Bureau
on November 21, 2012.

608
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:36,120
This has been confirmed.

609
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:37,350
Regarding the controversial parts

610
00:29:37,350 --> 00:29:38,750
in Cangfeng operation,

611
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:39,920
particularly

612
00:29:40,480 --> 00:29:42,370
the questionable issues
in the series of activities

613
00:29:42,370 --> 00:29:43,370
at Jingang Wharf,

614
00:29:43,720 --> 00:29:45,720
this hearing has completed
the investigation,

615
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:47,550
inquiry, and verification.

616
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:50,070
After discussion and final ruling,

617
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:52,720
the results of this hearing are
as follows.

618
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:56,350
We fully affirm the contribution

619
00:29:56,350 --> 00:29:58,110
made by Comrade Jiang Cheng,
former Deputy Captain

620
00:29:58,110 --> 00:30:01,270
of the Criminal Investigation Brigade 2
of Fengzhou District, Haizhou City,

621
00:30:01,270 --> 00:30:03,720
in investigating the illegal trading chain

622
00:30:03,720 --> 00:30:04,810
in Jin-Hai.

623
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:08,000
His suspected murder of Comrade Yao Weihai

624
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:09,930
and Comrade Meng Junfeng is

625
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:12,310
dismissed

626
00:30:12,910 --> 00:30:14,510
for insufficient evidence.

627
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:48,690
Jiang Cheng!

628
00:30:48,760 --> 00:30:49,490
Jiang Cheng.

629
00:30:49,620 --> 00:30:50,440
Don't be in a hurry to leave.

630
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:51,630
Wait here for a bit.

631
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:58,730
What did you say? Someone is coming?

632
00:31:01,070 --> 00:31:02,800
Yes... Yes, someone is coming.

633
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:06,100
Here she comes.

634
00:31:12,950 --> 00:31:14,450
A new police uniform is prepared for you.

635
00:31:14,450 --> 00:31:15,310
Go get changed.

636
00:31:19,080 --> 00:31:19,830
May I ask

637
00:31:19,830 --> 00:31:21,590
who prepared it for me?

638
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:22,960
Chief Tan.

639
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:25,310
Okay.

640
00:31:26,600 --> 00:31:27,640
Hurry up and get changed.

641
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:29,440
Someone's waiting downstairs.

642
00:31:29,550 --> 00:31:31,010
Someone is waiting for me?

643
00:31:33,210 --> 00:31:33,600
Yeah,

644
00:31:33,630 --> 00:31:35,660
I should get changed first.

645
00:31:54,590 --> 00:31:55,070
Dad.

646
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:57,750
Mom.

647
00:32:01,790 --> 00:32:02,350
I...

648
00:32:02,540 --> 00:32:03,390
I'm back.

649
00:32:24,710 --> 00:32:25,470
I'm sorry.

650
00:32:31,270 --> 00:32:32,800
It's good that you're back.

651
00:32:42,350 --> 00:32:43,950
You must have suffered a lot.

652
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:50,160
Mom.

653
00:32:58,830 --> 00:32:59,880
I missed you.

654
00:33:08,130 --> 00:33:09,040
Cheng,

655
00:33:10,070 --> 00:33:11,480
why didn't you tell us

656
00:33:12,810 --> 00:33:14,940
before doing something so dangerous?

657
00:33:17,130 --> 00:33:19,610
Captain Tan told us everything.

658
00:33:21,890 --> 00:33:23,930
I didn't handle it well.

659
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,400
You...

660
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:33,980
What are you doing?

661
00:33:36,110 --> 00:33:37,370
None of your business.

662
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:39,780
You came to see me empty-handed?

663
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:49,280
Why didn't you just die out there?

664
00:33:49,790 --> 00:33:51,050
I was lucky to survive.

665
00:33:51,290 --> 00:33:52,480
How's your hot pot restaurant doing?

666
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:53,550
Has it gone bankrupt?

667
00:33:53,550 --> 00:33:55,350
It became a chain a long time ago.

668
00:33:55,680 --> 00:33:57,010
Good thing you're back!

669
00:33:57,570 --> 00:33:58,440
Now,

670
00:33:58,660 --> 00:34:00,390
you can see how successful I am.

671
00:34:00,590 --> 00:34:01,240
Fine.

672
00:34:01,800 --> 00:34:03,530
You're doing pretty well, huh?

673
00:34:07,790 --> 00:34:08,480
Hey, bro.

674
00:34:08,500 --> 00:34:09,300
What's wrong?

675
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:10,670
Don't put on an act.

676
00:34:10,670 --> 00:34:11,280
I'm fine.

677
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:13,550
I'll live a long life.

678
00:34:13,550 --> 00:34:14,920
I'm waiting to inherit
your hot pot restaurant

679
00:34:14,920 --> 00:34:16,380
and enjoy a peaceful life.

680
00:34:17,409 --> 00:34:18,260
You?

681
00:34:19,510 --> 00:34:20,840
With your personality,

682
00:34:21,030 --> 00:34:22,090
you're like a fool.

683
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:24,400
I'll outlive you.

684
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:28,440
Cheng,

685
00:34:29,380 --> 00:34:30,380
welcome back!

686
00:34:38,290 --> 00:34:39,350
Alright, don't...

687
00:34:39,460 --> 00:34:40,719
Don't be sentimental.

688
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:41,590
Stop it.

689
00:34:41,590 --> 00:34:43,389
I'll beat you if you keep this up.

690
00:34:43,770 --> 00:34:45,250
You want to beat me?

691
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:46,030
You're getting cocky, huh?

692
00:34:46,030 --> 00:34:47,480
Come on.

693
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,400
Come on.

694
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:17,440
I'm relieved just to see you.

695
00:35:18,030 --> 00:35:20,030
-I'm actually doing fine.
-I know.

696
00:35:20,230 --> 00:35:20,960
Zhou!

697
00:35:22,710 --> 00:35:23,710
Welcome.

698
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:24,710
Welcome.

699
00:35:24,730 --> 00:35:25,700
Thank you for your hard work.

700
00:35:25,700 --> 00:35:27,300
-Have a seat, please.
-Okay.

701
00:35:28,550 --> 00:35:29,760
We're truly sorry.

702
00:35:30,070 --> 00:35:31,550
Right now, the main culprits

703
00:35:31,550 --> 00:35:32,840
involved in this case

704
00:35:33,030 --> 00:35:34,440
still haven't been arrested.

705
00:35:34,440 --> 00:35:35,100
Currently,

706
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:36,920
Jiang Cheng is a key witness,

707
00:35:36,920 --> 00:35:37,450
so

708
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:39,880
he can't be completely free for now.

709
00:35:40,480 --> 00:35:40,840
Wait,

710
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:43,240
we just want to have
a family meal together.

711
00:35:43,510 --> 00:35:44,880
Follow the leader's order.

712
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:45,800
We understand.

713
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:48,190
Seeing this kid safe and sound

714
00:35:48,190 --> 00:35:49,360
just puts our minds at ease.

715
00:35:49,360 --> 00:35:49,760
Yeah.

716
00:35:50,030 --> 00:35:51,710
We'll go see Zhou Jin later

717
00:35:52,030 --> 00:35:53,480
and then head back early.

718
00:35:54,860 --> 00:35:55,210
Good.

719
00:35:55,480 --> 00:35:56,110
Jin!

720
00:36:03,920 --> 00:36:04,630
Jin,

721
00:36:05,190 --> 00:36:06,240
look at Cheng.

722
00:36:06,440 --> 00:36:08,700
He looks best in a police uniform, right?

723
00:36:17,630 --> 00:36:18,320
Mom, Dad.

724
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:21,490
Why didn't you tell me you were coming?

725
00:36:22,260 --> 00:36:24,920
We wanted to see Jiang Cheng
as soon as possible,

726
00:36:24,970 --> 00:36:27,050
so we asked Bin to drive us here.

727
00:36:27,140 --> 00:36:28,440
It's fine. We wanted you
to focus on your own work.

728
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:29,600
Have you seen a doctor?

729
00:36:29,600 --> 00:36:31,000
Yes, it's nothing serious.

730
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:31,710
This girl.

731
00:36:32,190 --> 00:36:32,840
All right.

732
00:36:33,070 --> 00:36:35,330
I'll leave you to chat with your parents.

733
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:37,050
Jiang Cheng,

734
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:38,560
come out for a moment.

735
00:36:55,390 --> 00:36:59,530
[Captain's Office]

736
00:36:58,760 --> 00:36:59,220
Come in.

737
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:03,290
Sit down.

738
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:03,880
Okay.

739
00:37:06,590 --> 00:37:07,440
Actually,

740
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:09,460
there's nothing special.

741
00:37:10,320 --> 00:37:12,460
Since you are a key witness,

742
00:37:13,230 --> 00:37:14,360
the team has decided

743
00:37:14,590 --> 00:37:15,990
to arrange a dorm for you.

744
00:37:16,480 --> 00:37:17,210
In addition,

745
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:19,160
we'll assign someone

746
00:37:19,670 --> 00:37:21,920
to specifically take care
of your daily needs.

747
00:37:21,920 --> 00:37:22,520
Thank you.

748
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:24,980
In terms of safety,

749
00:37:25,230 --> 00:37:26,450
you need to be vigilant

750
00:37:26,450 --> 00:37:27,780
and careful on your own.

751
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:29,920
Does being a witness mean

752
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:31,300
I cannot be reinstated?

753
00:37:31,840 --> 00:37:33,550
You can't be reinstated for now.

754
00:37:33,550 --> 00:37:34,950
How long do I have to wait?

755
00:37:36,710 --> 00:37:37,910
Let me put it this way.

756
00:37:38,670 --> 00:37:40,470
About your identity as Cangfeng

757
00:37:40,550 --> 00:37:41,190
and

758
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:43,490
your contributions to intelligence,

759
00:37:43,710 --> 00:37:44,510
I believe

760
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:46,400
the higher-ups will highly value...

761
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:47,730
I want to hear the "but."

762
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:51,480
But

763
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:54,960
you only had one contact person.

764
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:57,540
Also, the only person who knew

765
00:37:57,630 --> 00:38:00,560
the details of your movements was
Leader Yao, right?

766
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:02,440
Besides,

767
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:04,880
you were in the crime syndicate

768
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:06,070
for such a long time,

769
00:38:06,360 --> 00:38:07,690
got involved so deeply,

770
00:38:08,480 --> 00:38:10,140
and reached such a high level.

771
00:38:10,550 --> 00:38:11,410
Think about it.

772
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,440
So the screening process

773
00:38:13,460 --> 00:38:15,320
will be relatively more complex.

774
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:16,130
What's more,

775
00:38:16,550 --> 00:38:18,680
the fact that you took Lu Pengfei's gun

776
00:38:18,710 --> 00:38:20,070
must also be evaluated.

777
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:22,970
The result may be different

778
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:25,190
from what you expect.

779
00:38:33,760 --> 00:38:34,590
I get it.

780
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:38,270
Some undercover cops turn bad
and become double agents,

781
00:38:38,270 --> 00:38:38,840
right?

782
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:42,300
You could understand it that way.

783
00:38:42,390 --> 00:38:43,480
Don't take it personally.

784
00:38:43,480 --> 00:38:45,010
It's a standard procedure.

785
00:38:45,430 --> 00:38:46,290
Yes, standard.

786
00:38:46,410 --> 00:38:48,000
Here you are, the dorm key.

787
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:52,250
I want to go home.

788
00:38:52,960 --> 00:38:54,360
Didn't I just tell you?

789
00:38:54,710 --> 00:38:55,760
You can't for now.

790
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:57,360
Our case is still...

791
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:57,960
Chief Tan,

792
00:38:58,590 --> 00:38:59,850
I won't leave Haizhou.

793
00:39:00,030 --> 00:39:01,840
I'll just go back to my old house.

794
00:39:01,860 --> 00:39:02,640
It's not far away.

795
00:39:02,640 --> 00:39:04,170
It's right in Jinze Garden.

796
00:39:05,710 --> 00:39:06,110
Okay.

797
00:39:07,190 --> 00:39:08,250
I can agree to that.

798
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:11,160
As for the one assigned to look after me,

799
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:12,570
I'd choose Zhou Jin.

800
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:16,460
Don't worry,
I won't be too much trouble for her.

801
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:19,160
Wait, do you think that's appropriate?

802
00:39:19,390 --> 00:39:21,250
You can ask for her opinion first.

803
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:29,230
Jin,

804
00:39:30,230 --> 00:39:31,480
tell your man

805
00:39:32,290 --> 00:39:33,810
to drive over

806
00:39:34,110 --> 00:39:35,570
and take the goodies back.

807
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,440
Last time I saw Hansheng,

808
00:39:37,590 --> 00:39:38,840
he seemed to like rice cakes,

809
00:39:38,840 --> 00:39:40,190
so I brought some extra.

810
00:39:40,630 --> 00:39:41,280
No problem.

811
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:42,550
I drove today.

812
00:39:42,590 --> 00:39:44,050
I'll take them back later.

813
00:39:44,630 --> 00:39:45,960
Call him out for dinner.

814
00:39:46,150 --> 00:39:47,950
Okay, I'll call him.

815
00:40:02,550 --> 00:40:03,190
Hansheng?

816
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:08,030
My parents are in Haizhou.

817
00:40:08,030 --> 00:40:10,090
Let's have dinner together tonight.

818
00:40:11,070 --> 00:40:13,800
My dad and Mrs. Fang
came back from abroad yesterday.

819
00:40:13,800 --> 00:40:16,330
I might need to have dinner
with them tonight.

820
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:18,610
What a coincidence.

821
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:22,280
All right then.

822
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,810
Let's split up for tonight.

823
00:40:28,700 --> 00:40:30,300
Are you coming home tonight?

824
00:40:31,570 --> 00:40:32,780
Hard to say.

825
00:40:32,840 --> 00:40:33,860
I might be home

826
00:40:34,260 --> 00:40:35,220
a bit late.

827
00:40:38,310 --> 00:40:38,910
Okay.

828
00:40:56,580 --> 00:40:58,500
Is Hansheng tied up?

829
00:40:59,980 --> 00:41:00,820
It just so happens

830
00:41:00,820 --> 00:41:03,080
that his dad and Mrs. Fang are
back from abroad.

831
00:41:03,080 --> 00:41:04,880
They are having dinner tonight, too.

832
00:41:04,880 --> 00:41:06,000
Girl,

833
00:41:06,340 --> 00:41:07,400
you should have added

834
00:41:07,400 --> 00:41:08,740
that we could all have dinner together.

835
00:41:08,740 --> 00:41:09,740
We are all family.

836
00:41:13,670 --> 00:41:14,400
Sir,

837
00:41:15,260 --> 00:41:17,220
I'm not part of your family.

838
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:19,110
We didn't mean that.

839
00:41:19,110 --> 00:41:20,630
Come on, I can tell it.

840
00:41:22,630 --> 00:41:23,360
Jin,

841
00:41:23,960 --> 00:41:25,150
you and Hansheng are

842
00:41:25,200 --> 00:41:26,730
not having a fight, are you?

843
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:28,550
No.

844
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:29,800
Why would we?

845
00:41:31,630 --> 00:41:32,190
Madam,

846
00:41:33,110 --> 00:41:34,200
if a couple

847
00:41:34,460 --> 00:41:35,460
never has a fight,

848
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,550
that's even a bigger problem.

849
00:41:37,550 --> 00:41:38,760
Shut up.

850
00:41:38,780 --> 00:41:40,480
I didn't tell him you were here.

851
00:41:40,480 --> 00:41:41,320
If I did,

852
00:41:41,320 --> 00:41:42,720
there's no way he'd come.

853
00:41:43,510 --> 00:41:44,110
Sir.

854
00:41:45,060 --> 00:41:46,120
Your son-in-law is

855
00:41:46,300 --> 00:41:47,130
incredibly

856
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:48,190
petty.

857
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:49,850
Shut up.

858
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:50,960
Stop holding my dad

859
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:52,360
and badmouthing others.

860
00:41:53,630 --> 00:41:54,230
Jin.

861
00:41:55,360 --> 00:41:56,110
tell me.

862
00:41:56,710 --> 00:41:58,110
Does he know you once were

863
00:41:58,510 --> 00:41:59,840
engaged to Jiang Cheng?

864
00:42:02,090 --> 00:42:03,350
I told him everything.

865
00:42:03,540 --> 00:42:05,190
You are usually too busy with work,

866
00:42:05,190 --> 00:42:05,980
but

867
00:42:06,070 --> 00:42:08,270
you need to balance it with your family.

868
00:42:08,510 --> 00:42:09,360
You can't let

869
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:11,610
Hansheng take care of you all the time.

870
00:42:13,190 --> 00:42:14,990
We're taking care of each other.

871
00:42:15,710 --> 00:42:16,360
Alright.

872
00:42:16,680 --> 00:42:17,400
Qiuyun,

873
00:42:17,840 --> 00:42:19,630
I think we should go back first.

874
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:20,840
Go back?

875
00:42:21,400 --> 00:42:22,480
Not staying for dinner?

876
00:42:22,480 --> 00:42:23,410
Forget about it.

877
00:42:23,510 --> 00:42:24,760
It'll get dark if we stay for dinner.

878
00:42:24,760 --> 00:42:26,440
Bin will be tired from driving.

879
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:27,500
I'm not tired, sir.

880
00:42:27,670 --> 00:42:28,270
Not tired.

881
00:42:29,630 --> 00:42:30,360
Zhou Jin.

882
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:32,510
You should go home early today, too.

883
00:42:32,510 --> 00:42:34,170
His parents are back in China.

884
00:42:34,590 --> 00:42:35,440
You should

885
00:42:35,790 --> 00:42:37,390
visit them from time to time.

886
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:38,710
Got it, Dad.

887
00:42:39,410 --> 00:42:40,110
By the way,

888
00:42:40,280 --> 00:42:42,210
do we still have any waxberry wine?

889
00:42:42,230 --> 00:42:43,880
Hansheng has been craving it.

890
00:42:43,880 --> 00:42:44,770
Yes, we do.

891
00:42:44,840 --> 00:42:46,280
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

892
00:42:46,280 --> 00:42:48,010
I could have brought some over.

893
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:49,150
I forgot.

894
00:42:49,150 --> 00:42:50,780
And I didn't know you were coming today.

895
00:42:50,780 --> 00:42:51,380
It's fine.

896
00:42:51,390 --> 00:42:54,060
I'll bring him over to have some
when he goes back.

897
00:42:54,060 --> 00:42:54,870
I'm back.
